&lt;h4&gt;TIP 직업별 능력치 보정 비교표&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;table_box&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(남성 캐릭터 전용)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;프리&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;3 / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / &lt;b&gt;(방어)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (마력)■&amp;times;1 / (마방)■&amp;times;3 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;용사&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;3 / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / (공격)■&amp;times;3 / (방어)■&amp;times;3 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;3 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;소환&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;3 / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / (공격)■&amp;times;1 / (방어)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(마력)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / &lt;b&gt;(마방)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;도지&lt;/b&gt; : &lt;b&gt;(HP)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / (MP)■&amp;times;1 / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / (방어)■&amp;times;3 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;2 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;택시&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(MP)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / (공격)■&amp;times;3 / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;2 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;형사&lt;/b&gt; : &lt;b&gt;(HP)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / &lt;b&gt;(방어)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (마력)■&amp;times;2 / (마방)■&amp;times;3 / (순발)■&amp;times;1&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;히트&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(MP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (공격)■&amp;times;3 / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(순발)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;노숙&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(MP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (공격)■&amp;times;1 / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(마력)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / &lt;b&gt;(마방)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;마피&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;3 / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / &lt;b&gt;(방어)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;1 / (순발)■&amp;times;2&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- ※프리터 / 용사 / 소환사 / 도지마의 용 / 택시 드라이버 / 형사 / 히트맨 / 노숙자 / 마피아&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;(남성 공용)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;호스&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(MP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (공격)■&amp;times;2 / (방어)■&amp;times;1 / &lt;b&gt;(마력)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / &lt;b&gt;(마방)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;댄서&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;3 / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / (공격)■&amp;times;3 / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(순발)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;요리&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;3 / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(마력)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (마방)■&amp;times;2 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;무사&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;3 / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / &lt;b&gt;(방어)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (마력)■&amp;times;2 / (마방)■&amp;times;2 / (순발)■&amp;times;2&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;액션&lt;/b&gt; : &lt;b&gt;(HP)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (방어)■&amp;times;3 / (마력)■&amp;times;1 / (마방)■&amp;times;2 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;마린&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(MP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (공격)■&amp;times;3 / (방어)■&amp;times;3 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;3 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;서부&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(MP)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;2 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;와일&lt;/b&gt; : &lt;b&gt;(HP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / &lt;b&gt;(MP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / (방어)■&amp;times;1 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;1 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;풋볼&lt;/b&gt; : &lt;b&gt;(HP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (MP)■&amp;times;2 / (공격)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(방어)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / (마력)■&amp;times;1 / (마방)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(순발)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- ※호스트 / 댄서 / 요리사 / 무사 / 액션 스타 / 마린 마스터 / 서부의 총잡이 / 와일드 댄서 / 풋볼러&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;(여성 캐릭터 전용)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;재벌&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;3 / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / (공격)■&amp;times;3 / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(순발)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;어새&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;3 / (MP)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(순발)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;마담&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(MP)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / (공격)■&amp;times;3 / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;3 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- ※재벌가 아가씨 / 어새신 / 작은 마담&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;(여성 공용)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;아이&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(MP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (공격)■&amp;times;2 / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(마력)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (마방)■&amp;times;3 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;나이&lt;/b&gt; : &lt;b&gt;(HP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / (방어)■&amp;times;3 / (마력)■&amp;times;2 / (마방)■&amp;times;1 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;쿠노&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(MP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (공격)■&amp;times;3 / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / (마력)■&amp;times;3 / (마방)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(순발)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;키퍼&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;3 / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / (공격)■&amp;times;1 / (방어)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(마력)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / &lt;b&gt;(마방)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;트로&lt;/b&gt; : (HP)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(MP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (공격)■&amp;times;3 / (방어)■&amp;times;2 / &lt;b&gt;(마력)■&amp;times;5&lt;/b&gt; / (마방)■&amp;times;2 / (순발)■&amp;times;3&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;테니&lt;/b&gt; : &lt;b&gt;(HP)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (MP)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(공격)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt; / (방어)■&amp;times;3 / (마력)■&amp;times;1 / (마방)■&amp;times;3 / &lt;b&gt;(순발)■&amp;times;4&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- ※아이돌 / 나이트 퀸 / 쿠노이치 / 하우스키퍼 / 트로피컬 댄서 / 테니스 플레이어&lt;/p&gt;
