&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;main_box&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;길거리 장기(박보)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;sub_box&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;알아두기&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;table_box&quot;&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;imageblock alignCenter&quot; data-ke-mobileStyle=&quot;widthOrigin&quot; data-origin-width=&quot;600&quot; data-origin-height=&quot;450&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-url=&quot;https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/bvmls5/btsJbtZLIa9/MumQlWQ3jPB34cP17bbTxK/img.jpg&quot; data-phocus=&quot;https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/bvmls5/btsJbtZLIa9/MumQlWQ3jPB34cP17bbTxK/img.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/bvmls5/btsJbtZLIa9/MumQlWQ3jPB34cP17bbTxK/img.jpg&quot; srcset=&quot;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdn%2Fbvmls5%2FbtsJbtZLIa9%2FMumQlWQ3jPB34cP17bbTxK%2Fimg.jpg&quot; onerror=&quot;this.onerror=null; this.src='//t1.daumcdn.net/tistory_admin/static/images/no-image-v1.png'; this.srcset='//t1.daumcdn.net/tistory_admin/static/images/no-image-v1.png';&quot; alt=&quot;길거리 장기 하와이 이미지&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;450&quot; data-origin-width=&quot;600&quot; data-origin-height=&quot;450&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;imagegridblock&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;image-container&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-url=&quot;https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/brstdb/btsJbhSUQWN/dURAHzoBU4LBJMQyGrgZMk/img.jpg&quot; data-phocus=&quot;https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/brstdb/btsJbhSUQWN/dURAHzoBU4LBJMQyGrgZMk/img.jpg&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; data-is-animation=&quot;false&quot; data-origin-width=&quot;600&quot; data-origin-height=&quot;532&quot; style=&quot;width: 55.0559%; margin-right: 10px;&quot; data-widthpercent=&quot;55.7&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/brstdb/btsJbhSUQWN/dURAHzoBU4LBJMQyGrgZMk/img.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;길거리 장기 이진쵸 이미지&quot; srcset=&quot;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;amp;fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdn%2Fbrstdb%2FbtsJbhSUQWN%2FdURAHzoBU4LBJMQyGrgZMk%2Fimg.jpg&quot; onerror=&quot;this.onerror=null; this.src='//t1.daumcdn.net/tistory_admin/static/images/no-image-v1.png'; this.srcset='//t1.daumcdn.net/tistory_admin/static/images/no-image-v1.png';&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;532&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-url=&quot;https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/SKhHs/btsJcQzAACe/D2xUNgj8dXKrkVUTzhGuVK/img.jpg&quot; data-phocus=&quot;https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/SKhHs/btsJcQzAACe/D2xUNgj8dXKrkVUTzhGuVK/img.jpg&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; data-is-animation=&quot;false&quot; data-origin-width=&quot;600&quot; data-origin-height=&quot;669&quot; style=&quot;width: 43.7813%;&quot; data-widthpercent=&quot;44.3&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://blog.kakaocdn.net/dn/SKhHs/btsJcQzAACe/D2xUNgj8dXKrkVUTzhGuVK/img.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;길거리 장기 카무로쵸 이미지&quot; srcset=&quot;https://img1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R1280x0/?scode=mtistory2&amp;amp;fname=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.kakaocdn.net%2Fdn%2FSKhHs%2FbtsJcQzAACe%2FD2xUNgj8dXKrkVUTzhGuVK%2Fimg.jpg&quot; onerror=&quot;this.onerror=null; this.src='//t1.daumcdn.net/tistory_admin/static/images/no-image-v1.png'; this.srcset='//t1.daumcdn.net/tistory_admin/static/images/no-image-v1.png';&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;669&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;- &lt;b&gt;해금&lt;/b&gt; : 제2장&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- 길거리 장기는 일본식 장기인 쇼기를 의미하며 한국식 장기와 비교했을 때 말의 이동, 세부 규칙 등이 모두 상이하기 때문에 제대로 하려면 처음부터 규칙을 숙지해야 하므로 진입벽이 있는 미니 게임입니다. 카지노, 도박장과 달리 포인트 구입이 없기 때문에 원하는 경품이 있다면 일종의 묘수풀이라고 할 수 있는 박보 장기를 도전해서 포인트를 버는 것을 생각해 볼 수 있습니다. 이 경우 초회 클리어 보상을 누적하면 약 1만 pts의 입수를 기대할 수 있습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
